value.0: Aye, <lad/lass>? Something I can do for ye? Has ye business with the guild?
Nay. Though them Cloakwizards have built an enclave in Neverwinter. I took a trip there once... 'tis a strange place, but Eltoora caters to wizardly folk.
The only temple in town is Tyr's, <lad/lass>.
If ye're askin' about odd things in Port Llast, hmmm... maybe ye should speak to Neurik at the temple. I hear the cleric has grave worries as o' late.
Me name be Kendrack, head of the guild, here, and mayor of Port Llast. Also known as the First Captain. That enough for ye?
Can one get magical supplies or identify items in town?
I'm looking for work, if you know of any.
